    <h2>
        Is there such a thing as an easy loan?
    </h2>
    <p>
        When people think of applying for a loan, the last thing that springs to mind is that it's going to be easy. In South Africa these days, easy loans are everywhere and readily available to anyone, which makes them… easy. But what is an easy loan? An easy loan can be virtually any type of loan from a lender as long as it's easily acquired. Some lenders will have easier loan options than others. <br><br>

        Easy loans don't put you through the hassle of paperwork, complicated terms and conditions, impossibly high qualification standards and/or credit checks when applying for the loan. Because an easy loan is not specifically one type of loan, you can consider it a loan that is quickly and easily obtained from a lender. <br><br>

        This means that it can be secured or unsecured: payday loans, debt consolidation, car or personal loans, amongst many others. <br> <br>

        For whatever reason you need a loan, find out what kind of loan would suit you best, because, at the end of the day, you're the one who will be making the repayments. A person with a bad credit record can also have access to cash with an easy loan. In many instances a credit check is not done with easy loans. Which is one of the reasons why it's… easy. <br><br>

        So, when you're in need of some extra cash and you don't want to go through a lot of drama, a smooth, trouble-free loan transaction looks appealing, doesn't it? Well, EcoGeneral is one of Nigeria most reliable and trusted short-term loan lenders. <br><br>

        We have been helping Nigerian's across the country make ends meet. As a uniquely Nigerian company, we are committed to responsible lending and advise to only borrow as much as you can afford to pay back. We offer minimal interest rates and maximum convenience. You apply, we deposit your money and you repay us when you next get paid. Easy. <br><br>

        We offer easy loans from &#8358;500 up to &#8358;3 000 with a capped 5% p/m interest rate; 100% paperless application; conveniently online; no faxing; no additional documentation required; instant qualification; and no extended waiting periods. And we ensure that you are paid on time, every time. It doesn't get easier than that! <br><br>

        Apply at EcoGeneral for peace of mind.
